1) REST API (по теме)

    Product (Товар)
POST /products — создать
GET /products — список
GET /products/{id} — один
PUT /products/{id} — обновить
DELETE /products/{id} — удалить
        
        Customer (Покупатель)
POST /customers
GET /customers
GET /customers/{id}
PUT /customers/{id}
DELETE /customers/{id}


        Purchase (Покупка)
POST /purchases — создать покупку (с product_id, customer_id)
GET /purchases
GET /purchases/{id}
PUT /purchases/{id}
DELETE /purchases/{id}